15c1b98feaf968dea82c6b3f61e35a11bd5dabec7ef7e2edaf29cf459b38711ee8162bb104fe2fb2a4089f5e543aa485ed9939bd817718776672c77a3806d695  0001-init-add-support-for-setting-a-filter-for-autdetect_.patch
"
